name: Puzzling Places - Patreon Legacy Support Version
summary:
THIS IS NOT THE MAIN PUZZLING PLACES APP!
Please check the regular Quest store for that.

This version of the app DOES NOT CONTAIN ANY PUZZLES!
It is solely intended to enable former Patreons to play the test puzzles that were released as part of the pre launch Patreon campaign as these are no longer supported by the main app. The Patreon test puzzles were exclusive for Patreon supporters and cannot be purchased anymore.

In order to install puzzles, please download and start the app once, then connect...
